Package jbt.execution.task.decorator

Class Summary
ExecutionDecorator Base class for all the ExecutionTask subclasses that are able to run decorator tasks (that is, classes that inherit from ModelDecorator).
ExecutionHierarchicalContextManager ExecutionHierarchicalContextManager is the ExecutionTask that knows how to run a ModelHierarchicalContextManager.
ExecutionInterrupter ExecutionInterrupter is the ExecutionTask that knows how to run a ModelInterrupter.
ExecutionInverter ExecutionInverter is the ExecutionTask that knows how to run a ModelInverter.
ExecutionLimit ExecutionLimit is the ExecutionTask that knows how to run a ModelLimit.
ExecutionRepeat ExecutionRepeat is the ExecutionTask that knows how to run a ModelForever.
ExecutionSafeContextManager ExecutionSafeContextManager is the ExecutionTask that knows how to run a ModelSafeContextManager.
ExecutionSafeOutputContextManager ExecutionSafeOutputContextManager is the ExecutionTask that knows how to run a ModelSafeOutputContextManager.
ExecutionSucceeder ExecutionSucceeder is the ExecutionTask that knows how to run a ModelSucceeder.
ExecutionUntilFail ExecutionUntilFail is the ExecutionTask that knows how to run a ModelUntilFail.
